title: When should the liquidity pool 2 be implemented?
body:
The liquidity pool 2 will allow holders to stake equal parts $SWEETS/ETH to earn additional $SWEETS. This will add liquidity to $SWEETS and increase their value. When should it launch? 

ASAP = in approximately 24 hours. The developers need time to implement the UI for staking $SWEETS. Please be patient.
